William Sanderson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Sanderson 0 William Sanderson (born January 10, 1944) is an American character actor famous for his roles in Blade Runner, Deadwood, True Blood, and as a cast member in the long-running 1980s television series Newhart.
